perl-Archive-Tar-Wrapper: perl-Archive-Tar-Wrapper (API wrapper around the 'tar' utility)
perl-Archive-Tar-Wrapper:
perl-Archive-Tar-Wrapper: Archive::Tar::Wrapper is an API wrapper around the 'tar' command line
perl-Archive-Tar-Wrapper: utility. It never stores anything in memory, but works on temporary
perl-Archive-Tar-Wrapper: directory structures on disk instead. It provides a mapping between
perl-Archive-Tar-Wrapper: the logical paths in the tarball and the 'real' files in the
perl-Archive-Tar-Wrapper: temporary directory on disk.
perl-Archive-Tar-Wrapper:
perl-Archive-Tar-Wrapper: Homepage: https://metacpan.org/release/Archive-Tar-Wrapper
